  "description": "<i>K?sh?nin DS</i> is a spin-off on a <i>K?sh?nin</i> TV series also known as <i>The Negotiator</i>. The lead actress in TV series is Reiko Usanagi (played by <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?developer=Ryouko+Yonekura\">Ryouko Yonekura</a>) who is a part of SIT (Special Investigations Team) that try to resolve criminal matters without bloodshed, in other words, with skilled negotiation techniques. The game, in turn, lets you experience just that by placing you in shoes of the SIT negotiator.<br><br>The game features live actors, including some of the cast from the TV series. Before you start negotiation, you must become familiar with the case and its facts. You must collect necessary information to be able to hold the upper hand during your conversation with the criminals. There are different outcomes to each negotiation and you must peruse criminal's tension level to best of your advantage.",
